# TableOfContents Component Rule

The [TableOfContents.vue](mdc:src/components/TableOfContents/TableOfContents.vue) component follows shadcn-vue conventions:

- It is a single file component (SFC) in the `src/components/TableOfContents` directory.
- Used for displaying a document outline or navigation.
- Uses Tailwind CSS for styling and utility classes.

For table of contents best practices, see the [shadcn-vue Tabs documentation](https://www.shadcn-vue.com/docs/components/tabs) as a reference for navigation components.
